      "content": "\u003cdiv class\u003d\"introduction img-head\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"header\"\u003e\n    \u003cimg src\u003d\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,\u003d\u003d\" alt\u003d\"App Icon\" /\u003e\n    \u003ch3\u003eWelcome to the Patent Evaluation Assistant!\u003c/h3\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \u003csection\u003e\n    \u003ch4\u003eOverview\u003c/h4\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003e\n      This AI-powered application analyzes a patent’s title and abstract to identify its core technologies, unique innovations, real-world use cases, and similar existing inventions. It outputs a structured HTML table with expert insights across technical, domain, and IP strategy perspectives.\n    \u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/section\u003e\n\n  \u003csection\u003e\n    \u003ch4\u003eInput\u003c/h4\u003e\n    \u003cul\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cstrong\u003epatent_title\u003c/strong\u003e (required): Title of the patent (e.g., \"AI-Driven Real-Time Object Detection\")\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cstrong\u003epatent_abstract\u003c/strong\u003e (required): A short summary of the invention and what it does\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cstrong\u003etech_domain\u003c/strong\u003e (required): The technology field (e.g., \"Computer Vision\", \"Blockchain\")\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cstrong\u003etarget_industry\u003c/strong\u003e (required): Industry where this patent would be used (e.g., \"Healthcare\", \"Automotive\")\u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\n  \u003c/section\u003e\n\n  \u003csection\u003e\n    \u003ch4\u003eOutput\u003c/h4\u003e\n    \u003cul\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eA structured HTML table with three expert sections:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePatent Analysis\u003c/strong\u003e: Highlights the core technologies, what makes the invention novel, and the problem it solves\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eReal-World Applications\u003c/strong\u003e: Lists practical use cases and explains how the patent supports them\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCompetitive Landscape\u003c/strong\u003e: Shows similar public patents or technologies with similarity scores and brief comparisons\u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\n  \u003c/section\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n",
